<p class="center small">✶  A Western North Carolina Landmark and a Family Link  ✶</p>

<p>
  In the landscape of western North Carolina, few places carry the historical weight of the
  Biltmore Estate near Asheville. For families rooted in Buncombe County and the surrounding
  communities, Biltmore represents not only a famous landmark but also a place where everyday
  lives intersected with one of the most ambitious estates in American history.
</p>

